ays a crucial\nrole in shaping the CMZ gas kinematics, and is a major contributor to\nsuppressing the SFR by inducing predominantly solenoidal turbulent modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2023 18:00:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
